name: Melffy Playground
effect: When this card is activated: You can add 1 "Melffy" monster from your Deck to your hand. Once per turn, during the Main Phase: You can place 1 "Melffy" Continuous Spell/Trap from your Deck or GY face-up in your Spell & Trap Zone.
